(249, 18, 'Which of the following does not apply to agility to a software process?', ' Uses incremental product delivery strategy', ' Only essential work products are produced', ' Eliminate the use of project planning and testing', ' All of the mentioned', 'Answer:c', 'Explanation: Testing is a major part of each software development process which can’t be avoided.'),
(250, 18, ' Which three framework activities are present in Adaptive Software Development(ASD) ?', ' analysis, design, coding', ' requirements gathering, adaptive cycle planning, iterative development', ' speculation, collaboration, learning', ' all of the mentioned', 'Answer:c', 'Explanation: None.'),
