(295, 19, '21.Architectural Design Metrics are ___________ in nature.', 'a) Black Box', 'b) White Box', 'c) Gray Box', 'd) Green Box', 'ANS: A', ' They are “black box” in that they do not require any knowledge of the inner workings of a particular software component.'),
