(1763, 49, '1 What is the output of the below Java program with a decrement operator and WHILE-loop? int a=4; while(a>0) { System.out.print(a + \" \"); a--; }', ' 4 3 2 1', ' 3 2 1', ' Compiler error', ' None', 'A', ''),
